    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i had a small cyst removed by my doctor a few days ago here in sydney. the cut looks a bit red and feels warm to the touch, and there is a little bit of yellow stuff oozing out of it. is that normal? can i just put some antibiotic cream on it and a warm compress to help it heal up?",
